This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and machine learning techniques for generating sketch portraits from photos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for representation learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of probabilistic fusion schemes, which is a technique commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) research.
